               <span>
                "Let's Fix It" Tour of College Campuses, February 21
               </span>
               <br/>
               <span>
                The UNC Charlotte Department of Political Science and Public Administration hosted a bipartisan conversation series with former
               </span>
               <span>
                Congressmen Patrick Murphy (Democrat) and David Jolly (Republican), who offered their diagnoses of what's wrong with Washington politics and solutions of what we can do...
